</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/ukermodean.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kermodean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Drunken Barbarian Harlot<br>...and don't call me Barbie</span><br> <font color=#FFAD18>(10/8/02 11:00:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/fhomeofordoursiprismatusfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.brunching.com/images/tina-dark.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Great Googa Mooga!!!!</span><hr size=1> re:Manaburn. You wouldn't believe the amount of problems this caused. A group of level 60 wizards with manaburn could actually taken down Trakanon. In a single volley. that's just silly. this was a good idea.<br>
<br>
re: Complete Heal - Not sure about this. Honestly, I'm not sure it's precisely a nerf, so much as a scaling down so that they can have a better heal in PoP. It isn't like clerics were hitting their 10k healing cap on that spell (up to 20k with a crit...that's just silly). expect to see an &quot;improved Complete heal&quot; in PoP that heals up to 10k. Let's face it, you'd have to be 65 just to have 10k hp. <br>
<br>
re: ModRods - This is the thing the mages on the mage board complain about second most. The only thing they complain about more is beastlords. Most raiding mages hate having to sit around and summon mod rods the entire 3 hour raid, because any other use of mana would be inefficient<br>
<br>
re: Monk - I'm not sure about this one. Everything they say makes sense, and it isn't really fair that monks can have the same AC as an equivalent warrior wearing big bulky armor and hitting for crap damage. This'll take some tuning, and will result in some yowling from the monks, but I can see where they're coming from. <p><img src=http://www.bearstuff.net/~aethercub/k-sig.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFD6A5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/uathairic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Athairic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>A moose bit my sister once.</span><br> <font color=#FFAD18>(10/8/02 11:15:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/fhomeofordoursiprismatusfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Great Googa Mooga!!!!</span><hr size=1> I am not sure how I feel about this.  Very mixed.<br>
